Prompting Style Workflow for Figma (Admin Side)

Access Control
- Prompt: "Design login/authentication flow for admins only. Show restricted access message for unauthorized users."

Main Dashboard
- Prompt: "Create a dashboard layout with live event status cards (Booked, Completed, Ongoing, Upcoming). Include a user count widget with drill-down details."
- Components: Event status tiles, user analytics chart, quick stats bar.

Vendor Management
- Prompt: "Design vendor management table with tabs for Approved, Rejected, Pending. Add controls to manually reassign vendors to events and edit vendor availability calendars."
- Components: Vendor list table, status filters, calendar editor.

Notifications
- Prompt: "Create a notifications panel with options to push General, User-specific, and Vendor-specific messages."
- Components: Notification composer, recipient selector, history log.

Issue Tracking & Metrics
- Prompt: "Design issue tracking board with ticket list, progress tracker, comment section, and email action button. Add real-time metrics widgets for revenue, engagement, and service ratings."
- Components: Kanban-style issue board, metrics dashboard.

Approvals
- Prompt: "Create approval page with vendor document viewer and Approve/Reject buttons."
- Components: Document preview pane, decision buttons, status history.

Event Management
- Prompt: "Design event management table with options to assign relationship managers, modify event details, or cancel events."
- Components: Event list, manager assignment dropdown, action buttons.

Promotional Push
- Prompt: "Create promotional management page with controls to set vendor display duration, publish ads/offers, and configure front-page banners/campaigns."
- Components: Campaign editor, scheduling calendar, banner preview.
